            <thetext>When you pass the image source into the constructor all stylesheet rules will 
be overwritten by the styles of the image:
var image = new qx.ui.basic.Image(&quot;sandbox/images/drawer.png&quot;);
image.setDecorator(&quot;toolbar-part&quot;);

When you define the image source in a setter everything works as expected:
var image = new qx.ui.basic.Image();
image.setDecorator(&quot;toolbar-part&quot;);
image.setSource(&quot;sandbox/images/drawer.png&quot;);</thetext>
